
Documentation: https://stripe.com/docs

PHP API Doc: https://stripe.com/docs/api/php

Customer -- Out Client (Company)

Charge -- Each charge of fees

Plan -- We have three plan (product)

Subscription -- Subscription of plan


Usage:

in config/main, add a key:

'params'=>array(
		'stripeKey' => 'xxxxxx',
),

in the controller or model, when you use it, please use:

$pay = new SpecifierPay(Yii::app()->params['stripeKey']);


